No. 156,

Misc.

Williams v. Illinois. Jack Greenberg, Michael Meltsner, and Stanley A. Bass for appellant. William J. Scott, Attorney General of Illinois, and James R. Thompson and Joel M. Flaum, Assistant Attorneys General, for appellee.

Appeal from Sup. Ct. Ill. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Probable jurisdiction noted and case transferred to appellate docket.
